0.3.0
=====
	* New features :
		* Video insertion
		* Backgrounds and gradients
		* Shapes
		* Async saving
		* UI enhancements (dialogs, progress bar)
		* SlideSorter view
		* Focus enhancements
		* Splitted core functionnality into ease-core
		* Foreach-enabled Clutter containers library (flutter)
	* Translations update (credits might be wrong)
